%N A028181 Expansion of 1/((1-5*x)*(1-7*x)*(1-8*x)*(1-10*x)).
%H A028181 Vincenzo Librandi, <a href="/A028181/b028181.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..900</a>
